  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Clean water for 11 970 students in Burkina Faso</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">This project will provide 11,970 students in 45 villages in Burkina Faso with 45 boreholes to make drinking water available. The action of Global NEEED Burkina will contribute to improve the living conditions of the population through the reduction of cases of water-related diseases, to reduce the time reserved for fetching water by women and children. It will also raise the school attendance. In short, this project will raise students&apos; school performance.</narrative>
  </description>
